If you're here, say something!

172
00:20:25,440 --> 00:20:27,850
I guess no one's here...

173
00:20:29,380 --> 00:20:31,290
Where?

174
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:36,340
Where did it go?!

175
00:20:36,840 --> 00:20:41,450
G-Gedatsu-sama. Y-Your eyes
are rolled inside your head.

176
00:20:41,450 --> 00:20:44,460
Y-You cannot see ahead of you like that.

177
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:45,800
How careless of me!

178
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:49,100
Have a look at this photograph.

179
00:20:50,160 --> 00:20:52,890
Here it is. That puny creature.

180
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:55,980
He's with the Blue Sea people!

181
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:59,650
What? It isn't a raccoon dog?

182
00:21:00,150 --> 00:21:03,420
Raccoon dog? No, it is not a wild animal.

183
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:07,530
It is unquestionably a
creature from the Blue Sea!

184
00:21:07,990 --> 00:21:12,040
Luffy! Where are you?!

185
00:21:12,040 --> 00:21:16,170
Zoro! Are you asleep again?!

186
00:21:16,170 --> 00:21:20,340
Robin! Hurry over here!

187
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:23,890
Where is everyone?!

188
00:21:23,890 --> 00:21:26,490
I'm feeling insecure!

189
00:21:26,490 --> 00:21:31,970
Hey! Guys! It's me!

190
00:21:38,800 --> 00:21:40,000
Where?!

191
00:21:53,650 --> 00:21:55,820
