207
00:23:25,570 --> 00:23:27,260
Are you a priest?!

208
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:31,090
This area is already my territory!
All around us are Swamp Clouds!

209
00:23:31,090 --> 00:23:32,330
There is no escape!

210
00:23:32,330 --> 00:23:35,260
Yeah! Everyone protects me
because I always run away!

211
00:23:36,180 --> 00:23:37,640
That's why they don't rely on me!

212
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:41,770
I'm going to raise a pirate flag
right here! I'm gonna beat him!

213
00:23:41,770 --> 00:23:43,040
On the next episode of One Piece!

214
00:23:43,040 --> 00:23:45,950
"The Ordeal of the Swamp!
Chopper vs. Sky Punk Gedatsu!!"

